reviewText: My wife and I have viewed and enjoyed every episode of Army Wives. It is the best series we've ever seen, and we always look forward to a new season. The characters are interesting and intriguing, the stories are realistic. Although I served in a different place and at a different time, I appreciate the service aspect of the series.

reviewText: The product arrived quickly and in good condition.Army wives is a fantastic series.  My granddaughter introduced me to Army Wives when her husband was deployed.  Her and all the other wives on base watched it together.  Very realistic - I can forgive that enlisted and officers spouses were close friends, because even though in reality, it isn't like that in the service - but it should be.

reviewText: i watched this first on amazon prime video.  Then I decided to go ahead and purchase the whole series.  This show is great.  It covers everything about what a family goes through in army life in all aspects.  You see it from the familys' view, you see it from the armys' point of view and all loved ones.  I love this show.  My grand-daughter is in the National Guards, and it really touched my heart for her.  She is just 17.  My father was a WWII War Veteran, I couldn't help but think of him while I was watching this show.  This show makes you laugh and cry.  Yet teaches you so much.  Love it.
